HEADWORD: Convocate
<hw>Con"vo*cate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Convocated</conjf>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
